sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Auth
    participant Integration
    participant AI
    participant Context
    participant Analytics
    participant DB

    %% Authentication Flow
    Client->>Gateway: Request Access
    Gateway->>Auth: Validate Credentials
    Auth->>DB: Check Credentials
    DB-->>Auth: Return User Data
    Auth-->>Gateway: Return JWT Token
    Gateway-->>Client: Return Access Token

    %% Message Processing Flow
    Client->>Gateway: Send Message
    Gateway->>Integration: Route Message
    Integration->>Context: Get Conversation Context
    Context->>DB: Fetch Context
    DB-->>Context: Return Context
    Context-->>Integration: Return Context
    Integration->>AI: Process Message with Context
    AI->>AI: Generate Response
    AI->>Analytics: Log Interaction
    AI-->>Integration: Return Response
    Integration-->>Gateway: Format Response
    Gateway-->>Client: Send Response

    %% Analytics Update
    Analytics->>DB: Store Metrics
    Analytics->>Analytics: Update Real-time Dashboard

    %% Context Update
    AI->>Context: Update Conversation Context
    Context->>DB: Store Updated Context